libnessy-client-perl (0.010-1) lucid; urgency=low

  * Implement new state machine based backend.
  * Added support for 'aborted' status on claims.
  * Timeout while waiting to get an active claim sets status to 'withdrawn'.
  * Unified handling of HTTP error responses.

